						               													<description>It&amp;rsquo;s time to put the cats away for the night. You&amp;rsquo;re throwing a dinner party, and your best friend&amp;rsquo;s spouse is allergic!&amp;#10;But making cats do what you want is never as simple as it should be.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of this push-your-luck, pickup-and-deliver game is to put all your cats upstairs at the same time for the night and get them to stay there while their mood swings. You do this by picking them up, but first you must distract them by appealing to their mood.&amp;#10;Each turn, all the cats will have their mood swings, and then move, act or react accordingly. Then, you can move around, opening and closing doors, moving toys and getting food and water where a cat will see it, and, if you played your odds right, pick up some cats to take them upstairs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But they won't stay forever there - if they feel strongly about something, they'll come downstairs again, looking to satisfy their urges. So, you need to hurry and put all the rest away quickly.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As if that wasn't enough, your time is limited, your visits are arriving soon, and if you don't manage to get all the cats before the mood cards run out, they'll crash your party the entire night. Good luck getting your guests to enjoy their dinner..!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;AWARDS&amp;#10;3rd place Best Overall Game in the 2021 Solitaire Print and Play Contest!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additionally:&amp;#10;- 1st place Best AI&amp;#10;- 1st place Best Regular PnP Build&amp;#10;- 3rd place Best Use of Theme&amp;#10;- 6th place Most Innovative Mechanics&amp;#10;- 6th place Best Original Art&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
